name: DPC 2023 WEU Summer Tour Division I – presented by PGL
description:
Dota 2 fans in Western Europe, get ready for an exciting tournament as the DPC 2023 Summer Tour is just around the corner! From May 15 to June 5, top teams from the region will battle it out for a chance to secure their spot in the third major of the season.

You won't want to miss a moment of the action as teams showcase their skills and strategies in thrilling matches. The DPC 2023 Summer Tour promises to be an unforgettable experience for Dota 2 fans in Western Europe.

Get ready to support your favorite teams as they compete for a chance to make it to the next major!
